VALUES
  ('social-worker-moex-02311', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Katz等學者試圖解構社會建構的異性戀概念，他們的觀點被視為「酷兒理論（queer theory）」，下列對 酷兒理論的敘述，何者錯誤？ 強調多元性 「酷兒」一詞原本是對同性戀者帶有貶損的稱呼 可以用來指稱跨性別者（transgender） 將性取向分為同性戀及異性戀，雙性戀者是對性取向欠缺認同者', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "200b3b0862fc", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe76495339a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "107", "s": "0605", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 39, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02312', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-0e79f916', 'sub-social-worker-01', NULL, 'single_choice', '大學生偉哲向社會工作師表達他對新戀情的困擾，因為他對最近認識的女友一見鍾情，雖然想要每天都 膩在一起，但並不想與她步入婚姻。社會工作師發現偉哲似乎有將女友過度理想化的情形，才交往一個 多月，對女友的描述多數是來自想像、猜測。若依據史登堡（Sternberg）愛情三角理論（triangular theory of love）來了解偉哲對女友的感情比較偏向下列何者？ 沒有愛情（non-love）    虛幻的愛（fatuous love） 伴侶的愛（companionate love）  迷戀（infatuation）', '["", "", "", ""]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, FALSE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "200b3b0862fc", "answer_pdf_sha1": "9fe76495339a", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "107", "s": "0605", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "人類行為與社會環境", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 40, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": ["incomplete_options"], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02313', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'essay', '現代社會充斥著「全球性的專制知識」（global unitary knowledge），讓你無從拒
