  ('social-worker-moex-02320', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', 'Mcleod和Meyer歸納出十組衝突的社會工作價值，下列何者不在這十組之列？', '["個人自由對社會控制", "異質性對同質性", "以個案為中心對以社區為中心", "相對實用論對絕對神聖論"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b8a3d37c0d1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5df06a1a485f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 6, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02321', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '社會工作理論不是由下列何者衍生而來的？', '["回應社會壓力", "透過一般民眾集結而成", "透過心智之眼建構出經驗體系的模式", "在歸納與演繹之間循環不息而致"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b8a3d37c0d1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5df06a1a485f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 7, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02322', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '「現代社會中，雖然貧窮或社會問題源於外在環境因素，但改變焦點還是應該放置在窮人及生活在某種 社會問題中的個人身上」。以上敘述，在本質上比較傾向下列那一種觀點持有者的說法？', '["多元文化", "責備受害人", "人道主義", "優勢取向"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b8a3d37c0d1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5df06a1a485f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 8, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('social-worker-moex-02323', 'social-worker', 'social-worker-moex-105-7c9828ae', 'sub-social-worker-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列何者對系統理論的描述是錯誤的？', '["系統有開放的和封閉的", "系統的成長越大時，其複雜性越強", "系統的完整是在不斷的演變中，為了維持其穩定與平衡，因此靜態的平衡是一種圓滿的狀態", "系統中的次系統之間的互惠性，若能維持協力共持的型態和結果，則可從外在環境獲得資源"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:12+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "9b8a3d37c0d1", "answer_pdf_sha1": "5df06a1a485f", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "107", "s": "0601", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "社會工作", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 9, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "socialworker", "db_exam_id": "social-worker"}'::jsonb, NULL),
